om\": 150, \"to\": 183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the first 'A' final of the night Shortt set a new Irish senior record as he Limerick swam 1:57.90, in the men's 200m backstroke, just .4 of a second shy of making the Olympic qualifying time (OQT).\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.99454519273557, \"rank\": 0.0030928412305485826, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"score\": 0.9964157198565164, \"rank\": 0.003427234067551459, \"text\": \"Limerick\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_FIBA_Men's_Olympic_Qualifying_Tournaments_\\u2013_Belgrade\", \"score\": 0.9176265664963549, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OQT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_FIBA_Men's_Olympic_Qualifying_Tournaments_\\u2013_Belgrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_FIBA_Men's_Olympic_Qualifying_Tournaments_\\u2013_Belgrade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first 'A' final\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 241}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"Shortt\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200m backstroke\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic qualifying time\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a thrilling finish, Shortt held off the challenge of Gavin Keogh and while was disappointed to have missed out on qualification time, the Galwayman will have another opportunity in the Super final on Saturday evening.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 641, \"entities